## ­¤ōŗ Project Context

This is **Hyperforce Runtime Platform 360 (HRP360)** - a dashboard for Salesforce's Hyperforce infrastructure monitoring.

**ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ IMPORTANT: This is a GitHub Pages project - NO React bundling. Use vanilla JavaScript only.**

### Feedback channel
- The **Slack logo** in the header links to **#hrp-360-support** ŌĆö the public channel where anyone can submit feedback for HRP 360.

### Current Dashboard Sections
| Section | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Onboarding** | FKP/Mesh adoption tracking, migration pipeline, service information |
| **Runtime Scale & Availability** | Autoscaling, Availability, Karpenter metrics |

### Removed Sections (no longer exist)
- ~~Cost to Serve~~ (removed)
- ~~Self Serve~~ (removed)

