## ­¤öæ Key Terminology

| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| **FKP** | Falcon Kubernetes Platform - managed K8s |
| **Mesh** | Service mesh (mTLS) |
| **HCP** | Hyperforce Control Plane |
| **HRP** | Hyperforce Runtime Platform |
| **Commercial** | Standard Salesforce cloud |
| **GIA/GovCloud** | Government cloud (FedRAMP) |
| **BlackJack** | DoD cloud - highest security |
| **HPA** | Horizontal Pod Autoscaler |
| **MTTD** | Mean Time to Detect |
| **MTTR** | Mean Time to Resolve |

### FKP Detection Logic
Instance is FKP if cluster name contains `"sam"` (case-insensitive)

### Migration Stages (1-6)
1. Not Started
2. Pre-Prod Progress
3. Parity Required
4. Prod Progress
5. Prod Complete
6. Mesh Complete

