## ­¤ÆĪ Key Functions in fkp-dashboard.js

### Tab Management
```javascript
switchTab(tabId)           // Switch to a tab
refreshCurrentTab()        // Refresh current tab content
switchViewMode(mode)       // Switch between 'exec' and 'developer'
```

### Data Loading
```javascript
loadAdoptionData()         // Load FKP adoption CSV data
loadAutoscalingData()      // Load Autoscaling.csv
loadAllAvailabilityData()  // Load all availability CSVs in parallel
```

### Rendering Functions
```javascript
renderExecutiveOverview()           // Onboarding overview (with metrics and roadmap)
renderOverallAdoptionMetrics()       // Commercial/GIA/Blackjack adoption cards
renderRoadmapTimeline()             // Leader/Cloud roadmap timeline
renderAICTA()                       // AI-generated calls to action
renderAutoscalingExecView()         // Autoscaling metrics cards
renderAutoscalingDeveloperView()    // Autoscaling services table
renderRuntimeAvailability()         // Availability (Exec View only - scrollable)
renderKarpenter()                   // Karpenter (routes to Exec/Dev view)
```

### Global State
```javascript
fkpDashboard.state.currentTab        // Current active tab ID
fkpDashboard.state.currentViewMode   // 'exec' or 'developer'
fkpDashboard.state.overviewViewBy   // 'org-leader', 'parent-cloud', or 'cloud' for roadmap
fkpDashboard.data.processed          // Processed adoption data
autoscalingData                      // Cached autoscaling data
availabilityData                     // Cached availability data
karpenterData                        // Cached Karpenter data
karpenterFilterState                 // Karpenter filter state
```

